name: Amber J
text: This is my favorite pizza in town. Im giving it 4 stars instead of 5 because unless you catch what you want on special the price is a bit much for a pizza you got inside a gas station. Also I don't think they deliver and that would be much more convenient.

name: Plankton
text: Kind people, rather cheap prices, and can usually find what you want. Also the menu is quite unique and nice

name: Phil Holloway
text: Awesome job guys!! Best pizza I've had in a long time!! Thanks!!

name: Jennifer Slone
text: The Godfathers pizza in Harrodsburg Ky is Excellent! Friendly workers an food is always fresh an Good:)
